{
  "stem": "19939.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And how did your family change after your mother's death?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother, I didn't realize was pregnant at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And probably in June or something, end of it, she took me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember taking me to the-- to the public school and to the principal, right, a woman.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she registered me to-- to first grade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I-- and then was-- this was before the vacation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I was taken away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know, to my-- her parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was there for the summer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were going a lot to grandparents for vacations or holidays.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and so I was-- I was there on vacation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was not aware of anything wrong in the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Nobody was saying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They didn't communicate with children much, you know, like it was in the old, you know, England, whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then I remember one think was Friday night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And although this what the Shabbat, my-- we were sitting in the kitchen and my grandfather came in through the door.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he said something in Yiddish that I didn't remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my grandmother started screaming that-- her mother-- and hitting her head against the wall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew that something terrible had happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I wasn't told about this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she died in the hospital in childbirth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She got, I think, blood poisoning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had no antibiotics, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But she was in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, you know, the funny thing that they didn't-- nobody explained to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is-- I stayed already there with my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody said anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was another cousin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were coming to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
